expatmm
------------------------------------------
ExpatMM XML Parser class for C++ based upon Expat.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libexpat1-2.8.0-1
  libexpatmm-devel-1.0.4-1bl2
  libexpatmm0-1.0.4-1bl2
  libgcc1-14.4.0-1
  libstdc++6-14.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-14.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-14.4.0-1
  libexpat-devel-2.8.0-1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/ckane/expatmm

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/ckane/expatmm/archive/refs/tags/1.0.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack expatmm-1.0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./expatmm-1.0.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/expatmm-1.0.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/expatmm-1.0.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libexpatmm0-1.0.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libexpatmm-devel-1.0.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(expatmm)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/expatmm.README
  /usr/share/doc/expatmm/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/expatmm/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/expatmm/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/expatmm/README-expatmm
  /usr/share/doc/expatmm/README.md

(libexpatmm0)
  /usr/bin/cygexpatmm-0.dll

(libexpatmm-devel)
  /usr/include/expatmm-1.0/expatmm/ExpatXMLFileParser.h
  /usr/include/expatmm-1.0/expatmm/ExpatXMLParser.h
  /usr/include/expatmm-1.0/expatmm/expatmm-libdef.h
  /usr/include/expatmm-1.0/expatmm/expatmm.h
  /usr/lib/libexpatmm.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/expatmm.pc

